A ranar Juma'a, daruruwan mutane sun taru a bakin rairayin bakin teku na garin Palu, inda raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi kusan mita shida (18ft) suka mamaye rairayin bakin teku, suna kashe mutane da yawa da kuma lalata duk abin da suka samu.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami.
"Lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta faru a jiya, mutane sun ci gaba da ayyukan su a bakin rairayin bakin teku ba tare da sun bar wurin ba, kuma sun zama wadanda aka azabtar", in ji Sothopo Pervo Ngroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar rage bala'in Indonesia, a wani taron tattaunawa a Jakarta.
"Tsunami bai zo shi kaɗai ba, ya ja motoci, tambura, gidaje, ya buge komai a ƙasa", in ji Nugroho, yana mai cewa tsunami ya zo ne a cikin teku mai nisa da saurin kilomita 800 a awa (497 mph) kafin ya kai gabar teku.
Ya ce wasu sun tsere ta hanyar hawa bishiyoyi domin su tsira daga tsunami.
