A lokacin da aka yi wa mutane da yawa annoba, sun yi ta taɓarɓarewa.
A ranar Juma'a, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami sun afkawa garin Palu na kasar Indonesia, inda suka kashe mutane 384, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu, in ji jami'ai.
"Saboda rashin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala, arewacin Palu, kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ba".
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin girgizar ƙasa da kuma guguwar tsunami, mutanen birnin suna bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwarsu.
Donggala yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin, yanki ne na yanki, wanda ke ƙarƙashin lardi, wanda ke da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kamfanin kamun kifi da noma sune manyan bangarorin tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiya na Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi yana da mahimmanci a Morowali a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce sunanan tsunami sun addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
Tsunami da ya auku a shekara ta 1938 ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 a Donggala kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje.
A shekarar 1996 kuma, tsunami ya afkawa yankin Donggala ta yamma, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ke fama da girgizar kasa a tekun Pacific kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa a kai a kai.
A cikin shekarun baya bayan nan, an yi wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin jihar Arche, a gabashin Sumatra, Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya mamaye kasashe 14, wanda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mazauna Arche.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, jerin girgizar ƙasa masu ƙarfi sun afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra.
An kashe daruruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin tsibirin Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, inda tsunami ya afkawa gabar tekun kudu, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidi Jayak na Achhe, inda ta haifar da bala'i da kuma ta'addanci ta hanyar tunatar da mutane game da mummunan bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a lokacin da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine, kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido cikin halin talala.
