Rahoton da 'yan tseren Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar ya nuna cewa an kama wani mutum mai suna Pauline, mai shekaru 29, a garin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, tsoma baki a cikin rahoton cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma tsayayya da kama.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, ya kwace wayar daga hannun wata mata da aka sani da laifin aikata laifuka, lokacin da ta yi kokarin tuntubar 'yan sanda.
