Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yanke wa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York hukuncin kisa.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York sun bukaci a yanke wa Saifullo Saipow hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, wanda ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953 saboda aikata laifi a karkashin dokar tarayya.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da amfani da motar haya don yin harin kan hanyar hawa keke a kan hanyar Manhattan ta Lower West Side a watan Oktoba don cin zarafin masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a kan hanyar.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su buƙaci tabbatar da cewa Sipov ya kashe "da gangan" wadanda aka kashe takwas, kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni ga jiki, bisa ga niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin New York.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, za a iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wani babban alkalin kotun tarayya ya zargi Saipov da laifuffuka 22, ciki har da aikata kisan kai guda takwas, wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin shari'o'in aikata laifuka da ake amfani da shi a cikin masu gabatar da kara na tarayya, da kuma amfani da motoci da karfi da lalata.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da ya dace da kuma shiri na farko", yayin da masu tuhumar suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi shi a matsayin "mai tashin hankali, mai zalunci da rashin mutunci".
"Safuolo Habilyevich Saipow ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Anne-Lore Decadette, Darren Drake, Ariel Arledge, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnuko rauni da kuma lalata iyalansu da abokansa", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kotun kotun kudancin New York.
An zargi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu dillalai biyu na miyagun kwayoyi, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A kotun tarayya da ke New York, an yanke hukuncin kisa na karshe a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, wanda aka zarge da laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yakin Cacar Shekaru biyu da suka gabata, a shekarar 1953.
A ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, aka kashe su biyu a kan kujera ta lantarki.
A cewar takardun kotu, wani dan kasar Uzbekistan mai suna Saipov, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa abin da ya yi daidai ne.
A cewar takardar tuhumar, Saipov ya shaidawa hukumomi cewa ya yi wannan harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon Isis a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin sa na asibiti.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, mai wakiltar Saipov a hukumar tsaro ta tarayya, ya ce "a bayyane yake cewa sun yi takaici" da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa maimakon amincewa da hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da damar samun 'yanci ba zai haifar da mummunan rauni ga duk wanda ke cikin lamarin", in ji Patten.
Kungiyar tsaron Saipov ta bukaci masu tuhumar da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
