A yanzu haka, Amurka ta ci nasara sau shida a jere a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar yayin da tawagar shugaban Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
